title: Flight Simulator 2020  - Addon spotlight - Kabul city
description:
In this addon spotlight we are going to look Kabul city which received an update which adds tons of point of interests. In this video we will take off from Kabul airport and will fly over the multiple POI's to give an impression what you can expect from this addon.

If you want to also add all the POI's which are shown in this video in that case download the addon via the link below:
https://flightsim.to/file/19350/welcome-to-kabul
